 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df296f859b9991607f14a6d3b689e6a5f2483a9c","tid":325484,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 雖然佢地係呃政治水<br />\n不過最有抗爭能力真係佢地</blockquote><br />\n重講抗爭? 想做永久反對派?<br />\n我地滿仔喺選舉論壇已經多番強調熱普城最堅嘅係執政能力啦"},{"pid":"cbdc2b8dc67ce81fc6bc8e88cf06f086ccd4a032","tid":325484,"uid":52651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 雖然佢地係呃政治水<br />\n不過最有抗爭能力真係佢地</blockquote><br />\n佢地有撚抗爭力，佢地發起過幾多次抗爭?"},{"pid":"8fb4afda94044f53b34236a797bb814dbfa0dba3","tid":325484,"uid":56311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 雖然佢地係呃政治水<br />\n不過<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最有抗爭能力</span></strong></strong>真係佢地</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16902e4cd0259796c0405326b5afb7f9792eac3","tid":325484,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:33:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91b3d753af81f7d86811cbbee680724e30400b9c","tid":325484,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T23:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 雖然佢地係呃政治水<br />\n不過最有抗爭能力真係佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱共"},{"pid":"b3365dd549c7cdfa9087477eb634b2eef6ea23c7","tid":325484,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T23:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曲到直</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高汁<img src=\"/ass